forecastTestType: Recommended based on minimum interval from invalid dose
generalDescription: This test case describes when a child receives the second dose of the Influenza vaccine at less than 4 weeks - 4 days from the previous dose, that the dose is not valid and a repeat dose should be recommended at 4 weeks later.
reasonForChange:
